@ChannelPipelineCoverage(value="one")
public class MessageDispatchHandler
extends org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler

The terminal upstream listener, which takes decoded messages (either WelcomeMessage or Message) and passes this information up to the MessageArrivalListener - typically, the NettyMessenger for this connection.
